EPISODE 35

4
00:00:19,029 --> 00:00:21,349
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shancai, why are you here?</b></font>

5
00:00:22,149 --> 00:00:23,669
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Aren't you off today?</b></font>

6
00:00:25,629 --> 00:00:28,749
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I just happened to pass by.</b></font>

7
00:00:29,589 --> 00:00:30,589
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm telling you.</b></font>

8
00:00:30,669 --> 00:00:32,029
<font color="#ffff00"><b>There are so many orders today.</b></font>

9
00:00:32,109 --> 00:00:33,509
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I can't handle it on my own.</b></font>

10
00:00:33,589 --> 00:00:35,189
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Our boss went out earlier.</b></font>

11
00:00:35,989 --> 00:00:37,189
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Do you still have a hangover?</b></font>

12
00:00:37,349 --> 00:00:38,629
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Come and help me for a while.</b></font>

13
00:00:39,909 --> 00:00:41,349
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Okay, sure.</b></font>

14
00:00:41,429 --> 00:00:42,509
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Go get changed.</b></font>

15
00:00:43,669 --> 00:00:44,509
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Okay.</b></font>

16
00:00:51,269 --> 00:00:52,349
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shancai.</b></font>

17
00:00:58,589 --> 00:01:02,109
<font color="#ffff00"><b>No matter what happens
to my family in the future,</b></font>

18
00:01:03,709 --> 00:01:05,829
<font color="#ffff00"><b>don't disappear on your own again.</b></font>

19
00:01:34,429 --> 00:01:37,149
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm happy that you and Daoming Si
are together.</b></font>

20
00:01:41,109 --> 00:01:43,189
<font color="#ffff00"><b>And I'm even happier to hear
about how you feel.</b></font>

21
00:01:45,349 --> 00:01:46,269
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm sorry.</b></font>

22
00:01:52,189 --> 00:01:53,029
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Thank you...</b></font>

23
00:01:54,589 --> 00:01:55,829
<font color="#ffff00"><b>for not giving up.</b></font>

24
00:02:42,309 --> 00:02:43,309
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Xiaoyou?</b></font>

25
00:02:46,269 --> 00:02:47,509
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why are you here?</b></font>

26
00:02:48,189 --> 00:02:49,389
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I was waiting for you.</b></font>

27
00:02:50,429 --> 00:02:52,309
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You just stood here and waited?</b></font>

28
00:02:56,189 --> 00:02:57,909
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It seems you like to surprise people.</b></font>

29
00:02:59,349 --> 00:03:01,909
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm sorry for doing this so suddenly.</b></font>

30
00:03:02,789 --> 00:03:03,829
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's all right.</b></font>

31
00:03:05,069 --> 00:03:07,309
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What if I didn't come home?</b></font>

32
00:03:08,309 --> 00:03:09,389
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Then I would have left.</b></font>

33
00:03:12,269 --> 00:03:15,149
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Actually, I'm here to apologize to you.</b></font>

34
00:03:15,709 --> 00:03:16,589
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Apologize to me?</b></font>

35
00:03:17,829 --> 00:03:19,909
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm sorry about yesterday.</b></font>

36
00:03:20,469 --> 00:03:22,789
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's okay. I'm used to it.</b></font>

37
00:03:23,749 --> 00:03:26,949
<font color="#ffff00"><b>If I worried about these things,
then I'd be really busy.</b></font>

38
00:03:28,069 --> 00:03:29,989
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I thought you'd be mad.</b></font>

39
00:03:30,629 --> 00:03:32,389
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It turns out you don't care.</b></font>

40
00:03:34,629 --> 00:03:37,589
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I thought I already caught your attention.</b></font>

41
00:03:38,069 --> 00:03:39,069
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Xiaoyou.</b></font>

42
00:03:41,309 --> 00:03:42,389
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Do you know</b></font>

43
00:03:43,189 --> 00:03:45,669
<font color="#ffff00"><b>why I never dated any girls
in Mingde University?</b></font>

44
00:03:47,589 --> 00:03:51,109
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Because they're too close.
So it'd be too irritating for you?</b></font>

45
00:03:51,669 --> 00:03:53,549
<font color="#ffff00"><b>That's right. You're very smart.</b></font>

46
00:03:54,949 --> 00:03:57,989
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You're Shancai's friend.
Shancai is my good friend's girlfriend.</b></font>

47
00:03:58,709 --> 00:04:01,549
<font color="#ffff00"><b>That means you're even
more irritating than Mingde's girls.</b></font>

48
00:04:04,229 --> 00:04:05,549
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Sorry to be so blunt.</b></font>

49
00:04:06,149 --> 00:04:10,109
<font color="#ffff00"><b>However, I think we'd be good as friends,
don't you think?</b></font>

50
00:04:13,549 --> 00:04:14,589
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's getting late.</b></font>

51
00:04:15,269 --> 00:04:17,749
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You should go home.
It might be dangerous later.</b></font>

52
00:04:18,469 --> 00:04:19,589
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I want it all.</b></font>

53
00:04:22,949 --> 00:04:27,509
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Last time, you said we can go on dates,
kiss and hug, right?</b></font>

54
00:04:29,429 --> 00:04:30,669
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You have to keep your word.</b></font>

55
00:04:33,069 --> 00:04:34,269
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Xiaoyou.</b></font>

56
00:04:34,789 --> 00:04:36,269
<font color="#ffff00"><b>When did you become so bold?</b></font>

57
00:04:36,909 --> 00:04:38,509
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You're brave enough to say these things.</b></font>

58
00:04:39,309 --> 00:04:40,829
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You weren't like that before.</b></font>

59
00:04:41,389 --> 00:04:42,949
<font color="#ffff00"><b>If I don't learn to say these things,</b></font>

60
00:04:43,949 --> 00:04:45,829
<font color="#ffff00"><b>how can I like someone like you?</b></font>

61
00:04:48,149 --> 00:04:51,069
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-But--
-Arrange your schedule then let me know.</b></font>

62
00:04:51,549 --> 00:04:54,349
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Sorry to disturb you today.
I'll leave now. Bye.</b></font>

63
00:05:46,309 --> 00:05:47,989
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Don't you have anything better to do?</b></font>

64
00:05:56,029 --> 00:05:58,509
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Welcome home. Shanghai welcomes you.</b></font>

65
00:06:01,789 --> 00:06:03,269
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Hey. Bottoms up.</b></font>

66
00:06:03,469 --> 00:06:05,509
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-I agree.
-Yes.</b></font>

67
00:06:14,669 --> 00:06:16,909
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I just got back
and you're treating me like this.</b></font>

68
00:06:17,709 --> 00:06:19,469
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why didn't you let us see you off?</b></font>

69
00:06:19,709 --> 00:06:21,029
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I felt so guilty all these months.</b></font>

70
00:06:22,029 --> 00:06:24,189
<font color="#ffff00"><b>One or two days in a few months
is more like it.</b></font>

71
00:06:25,589 --> 00:06:26,629
<font color="#ffff00"><b>One day.</b></font>

72
00:06:27,749 --> 00:06:29,629
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why are you taking turns
with Si to play cool?</b></font>

73
00:06:29,829 --> 00:06:31,709
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You feel like you're the only cool one.</b></font>

74
00:06:32,509 --> 00:06:34,669
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Playing it cool? I was born cool.</b></font>

75
00:06:34,829 --> 00:06:36,389
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Yes, you're the coolest.</b></font>

76
00:06:36,469 --> 00:06:37,429
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-The coolest ever.
-Cool.</b></font>

77
00:06:37,509 --> 00:06:38,389
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Are you as cool as me?</b></font>

78
00:06:39,549 --> 00:06:40,429
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Hey.</b></font>

79
00:06:41,589 --> 00:06:44,069
<font color="#ffff00"><b>How's your family situation?
Do you need any help?</b></font>

80
00:06:45,709 --> 00:06:46,589
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's fine.</b></font>

81
00:06:46,789 --> 00:06:49,469
<font color="#ffff00"><b>They told me to just study hard
and not to worry.</b></font>

82
00:06:51,589 --> 00:06:54,349
<font color="#ffff00"><b>So, are you willing
to come back to us now?</b></font>

83
00:06:55,189 --> 00:06:56,509
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I never left.</b></font>

84
00:06:57,429 --> 00:06:58,749
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You never left?</b></font>

85
00:06:59,589 --> 00:07:01,029
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Then drink some more.</b></font>

86
00:07:01,589 --> 00:07:02,429
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-Pour more.
-Here.</b></font>

87
00:07:02,509 --> 00:07:03,429
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Full glass.</b></font>

88
00:07:03,509 --> 00:07:05,309
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-Fill it up.
-Finish it all.</b></font>

89
00:07:06,269 --> 00:07:07,389
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-That's fine.
-That's enough.</b></font>

90
00:07:10,309 --> 00:07:11,149
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Drink it.</b></font>

91
00:07:11,749 --> 00:07:13,589
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Two seconds. Countdown.</b></font>

92
00:07:14,269 --> 00:07:15,109
<font color="#ffff00"><b>One.</b></font>

93
00:07:15,389 --> 00:07:16,309
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Two.</b></font>

94
00:07:16,629 --> 00:07:17,789
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You took too long.</b></font>

95
00:07:20,789 --> 00:07:21,749
<font color="#ffff00"><b>One more.</b></font>

96
00:07:27,949 --> 00:07:29,669
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Then let's toast to our friendship.</b></font>

97
00:07:30,309 --> 00:07:31,589
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Okay. Here.</b></font>

98
00:07:36,669 --> 00:07:38,669
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-Come on. Cheers.
-Cheers.</b></font>

99
00:07:39,229 --> 00:07:40,109
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Cheers.</b></font>

100
00:07:54,989 --> 00:07:55,989
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Do you know?</b></font>

101
00:07:58,189 --> 00:08:00,149
<font color="#ffff00"><b>If you don't, then ask me.</b></font>

102
00:08:00,669 --> 00:08:02,429
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I don't know but I don't want to ask you.</b></font>

103
00:08:04,909 --> 00:08:08,109
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why don't you have any curiosity
towards your friend?</b></font>

104
00:08:08,669 --> 00:08:09,589
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I really don't.</b></font>

105
00:08:11,029 --> 00:08:12,029
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I don't care.</b></font>

106
00:08:12,549 --> 00:08:13,549
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Ask me.</b></font>

107
00:08:14,229 --> 00:08:15,909
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Ask me how I'm doing lately.</b></font>

108
00:08:17,909 --> 00:08:20,629
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-You're doing great.
-Who told you that?</b></font>

109
00:08:21,269 --> 00:08:23,429
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-Aren't you doing great?
-I'm doing great.</b></font>

110
00:08:23,509 --> 00:08:24,429
<font color="#ffff00"><b>All right.</b></font>

111
00:08:28,189 --> 00:08:29,549
<font color="#ffff00"><b>He played me.</b></font>

112
00:08:32,949 --> 00:08:33,869
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Lei.</b></font>

113
00:08:34,229 --> 00:08:35,549
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Just do what he wants,</b></font>

114
00:08:35,629 --> 00:08:38,349
<font color="#ffff00"><b>or else he'll make a fuss all night.</b></font>

115
00:08:38,909 --> 00:08:40,069
<font color="#ffff00"><b>We all won't be able to sleep.</b></font>

116
00:08:40,629 --> 00:08:43,309
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Si, I told Lei as soon as it happened.</b></font>

117
00:08:44,949 --> 00:08:49,149
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Not just Ximen and Meizuo,
even Xiaozi told me about it.</b></font>

118
00:08:49,749 --> 00:08:51,589
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Three people. Three versions.</b></font>

119
00:08:52,229 --> 00:08:53,509
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I don't care.</b></font>

120
00:08:53,909 --> 00:08:56,109
<font color="#ffff00"><b>My version is the original one.</b></font>

121
00:08:58,069 --> 00:08:59,749
<font color="#ffff00"><b>And I want to tell you myself.</b></font>

122
00:09:01,069 --> 00:09:02,029
<font color="#ffff00"><b>All right.</b></font>

123
00:09:05,869 --> 00:09:08,909
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Si, how are you and Shancai?</b></font>

124
00:09:13,509 --> 00:09:15,149
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shancai and I are officially together.</b></font>

125
00:09:16,029 --> 00:09:17,149
<font color="#ffff00"><b>All right.</b></font>

126
00:09:20,069 --> 00:09:22,669
<font color="#ffff00"><b>We're together now.</b></font>

127
00:09:24,429 --> 00:09:25,549
<font color="#ffff00"><b>That's great!</b></font>

128
00:09:27,909 --> 00:09:28,789
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Si.</b></font>

129
00:09:30,429 --> 00:09:31,389
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Congratulations.</b></font>

130
00:09:33,349 --> 00:09:36,069
<font color="#ffff00"><b>This is great. F4 is now back to normal.</b></font>

131
00:09:36,269 --> 00:09:37,149
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm so moved.</b></font>

132
00:09:37,829 --> 00:09:40,469
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Cut the crap. Let's make a toast!</b></font>

133
00:09:40,549 --> 00:09:45,069
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Let's toast to Si officially being taken.
What do you think?</b></font>

134
00:09:45,549 --> 00:09:46,389
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Not bad.</b></font>

135
00:09:46,589 --> 00:09:47,709
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Come on. Cheers.</b></font>

136
00:09:47,789 --> 00:09:49,309
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-Cheers.
-Cheers.</b></font>

137
00:10:09,549 --> 00:10:10,549
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Lei.</b></font>

138
00:10:11,749 --> 00:10:13,389
<font color="#ffff00"><b>When did you come back to Shanghai?</b></font>

139
00:10:15,429 --> 00:10:17,109
<font color="#ffff00"><b>How's your family situation?</b></font>

140
00:10:19,989 --> 00:10:20,949
<font color="#ffff00"><b>How are you?</b></font>

141
00:10:22,709 --> 00:10:23,829
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why are you here?</b></font>

142
00:10:24,869 --> 00:10:25,749
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Yesterday.</b></font>

143
00:10:26,549 --> 00:10:27,389
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Good.</b></font>

144
00:10:28,589 --> 00:10:29,669
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Because I want to come here.</b></font>

145
00:10:32,989 --> 00:10:34,109
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why are you here?</b></font>

146
00:10:36,909 --> 00:10:38,869
<font color="#ffff00"><b>The same reason as you.</b></font>

147
00:10:43,149 --> 00:10:45,189
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's so good to have you back.</b></font>

148
00:10:46,189 --> 00:10:47,669
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What are your plans?</b></font>

149
00:10:49,069 --> 00:10:50,749
<font color="#ffff00"><b>To continue preparing for the recital.</b></font>

150
00:10:51,469 --> 00:10:52,429
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Really?</b></font>

151
00:10:53,349 --> 00:10:56,229
<font color="#ffff00"><b>That's great.
I'd love to hear you play the violin.</b></font>

152
00:10:57,469 --> 00:10:58,389
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Is that so?</b></font>

153
00:10:58,949 --> 00:10:59,789
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Yes.</b></font>

154
00:11:04,749 --> 00:11:05,749
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shancai.</b></font>

155
00:11:06,989 --> 00:11:09,589
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You and Si are officially together, right?</b></font>

156
00:11:12,229 --> 00:11:14,109
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I think it's a very good start.</b></font>

157
00:11:15,989 --> 00:11:16,909
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Yes.</b></font>

158
00:11:17,909 --> 00:11:19,829
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It just turned out this way.</b></font>

159
00:11:21,469 --> 00:11:23,669
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Actually, I have mixed feelings about it.</b></font>

160
00:11:24,589 --> 00:11:27,349
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm a little happy and a little sad.</b></font>

161
00:11:30,629 --> 00:11:33,029
<font color="#ffff00"><b>On one hand, I hope things
between you and Si go smoothly.</b></font>

162
00:11:34,149 --> 00:11:37,269
<font color="#ffff00"><b>On the other hand, you're special to me.</b></font>

163
00:11:38,389 --> 00:11:39,589
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Special?</b></font>

164
00:11:40,629 --> 00:11:41,669
<font color="#ffff00"><b>To put it bluntly,</b></font>

165
00:11:43,989 --> 00:11:46,269
<font color="#ffff00"><b>you're like my pet.</b></font>

166
00:11:46,909 --> 00:11:48,029
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Pet?</b></font>

167
00:11:51,309 --> 00:11:52,189
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Never mind.</b></font>

168
00:11:53,309 --> 00:11:55,309
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What do I expect you to say?</b></font>

169
00:11:55,869 --> 00:11:56,989
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You should be happy.</b></font>

170
00:11:58,389 --> 00:11:59,709
<font color="#ffff00"><b>We all should be happy.</b></font>

171
00:12:02,669 --> 00:12:04,269
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You're my good friend's girlfriend.</b></font>

172
00:12:05,349 --> 00:12:06,309
<font color="#ffff00"><b>This way,</b></font>

173
00:12:07,549 --> 00:12:09,069
<font color="#ffff00"><b>we can be friends forever.</b></font>

174
00:12:14,829 --> 00:12:15,789
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'll go to practice now.</b></font>

175
00:12:21,189 --> 00:12:22,029
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Lei.</b></font>

176
00:12:23,549 --> 00:12:25,349
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You know I liked you before, right?</b></font>

177
00:12:29,469 --> 00:12:30,989
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Goodbye, Shancai.</b></font>

178
00:12:36,269 --> 00:12:40,789
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>I was able to easily blurt out something
I've had a hard time saying before.</i></b></font>

179
00:12:42,109 --> 00:12:44,949
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>I'm happy when I heard Lei say,
"friends forever."</i></b></font>

180
00:12:46,029 --> 00:12:48,029
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>My first love has ended.</i></b></font>

181
00:12:49,149 --> 00:12:51,389
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>This is the moment when love
became friendship.</i></b></font>

182
00:12:53,789 --> 00:12:55,389
<font color="#ffff00"><b>NEW FRIEND</b></font>

183
00:12:56,149 --> 00:12:59,629
<font color="#ffff00"><b>XIAOYOU</b></font>

184
00:13:01,589 --> 00:13:03,189
<font color="#ffff00"><b>How are you lately, Master Ximen?</b></font>

185
00:13:04,189 --> 00:13:06,069
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm all right. Still the same as before.</b></font>

186
00:13:07,429 --> 00:13:08,309
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I guess so.</b></font>

187
00:13:08,789 --> 00:13:10,789
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Since your dad retired,</b></font>

188
00:13:11,349 --> 00:13:15,109
<font color="#ffff00"><b>you've been hosting
the tea ceremonies on your own.</b></font>

189
00:13:17,429 --> 00:13:19,469
